81
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:46,490
Still, you could have talked to her.

82
00:08:46,490 --> 00:08:47,920
What's wrong with you?

83
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,860
What do you mean?

84
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:53,560
Have some common courtesy.

85
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,730
Courtesy?

86
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,800
