184
00:15:34,260 --> 00:15:35,260
Seems like

185
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:38,300
I need your permission to get off.

186
00:15:39,370 --> 00:15:40,370
Yeah...

187
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:42,840
It would be

188
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,140
problematic if you stop me again.

189
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:54,410
I understand.

190
00:15:54,410 --> 00:15:57,320
When a person is extremely sad,

191
00:15:57,320 --> 00:16:00,350
they want to lean on a stranger.

192
00:16:02,290 --> 00:16:03,520
What I'm saying is,

193
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:08,160
you don't have to feel embarrassed.

194
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:11,300
So.

195
00:16:12,770 --> 00:16:14,570
Can I get off

196
00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:17,200
at the next stop?

197
00:16:21,940 --> 00:16:23,640
Is that a yes?

198
00:16:29,919 --> 00:16:31,050
Then...

199
00:16:33,850 --> 00:16:35,090
The bell.

200
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:12,730
If you have more to say,

201
00:17:12,730 --> 00:17:14,730
